==Swedish==

===Verb===
{{sv-verb-reg-er|stem=tänk|endstart=t}}
'''tänka'''

# [[think]]; to [[ponder]], to communicate to oneself in one's mind
# [[intend]]; to [[plan on]]; to mean
#:''Jag '''tänker''' åka utomlands på semestern'' = ''I mean to go abroad during the vacation''

====Synonyms====
;think
* [[fundera]]
;intend
* [[mena]]

